show.description:
Happily Never After follows Rajveer Singhania, whose life spirals into chaos when his fiancée Veda Mehta mistakes his pregnant sister-in-law Shanaya Birla for his mistress. 
What starts as a misunderstanding at an engagement turns into a dark, twisted tale of betrayal, violence, and shocking truths.
